p: The concentration of triethylene glycol dimethacrylate (TEGDMA), diurethane dimethacrylate (DUDMA), and bisphenol-A-glycidyl-methacrylate (bis-GMA) released into the ethanol was quantified before and after each analysis and compared to the values of a calibration line, previously created using standard solutions (Sigma Aldrich, Milan, Italy).
